<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.2.7">
<l>maṭantaiyai vaṇkama lattiru mātiṉai</l>
<l>taṭaṅkoṭṭār mārpiṉil vaittavar tāḷiṉmēl</l>
<l>vaṭaṅkoḷpūn taṇṇan tuḻāymalark kēyivaḷ</l>
<l>maṭaṅkumāl, vāṇuta līreṉ maṭakkompē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To the cool Tulsi blossoms with flowers in [several] strands</l>
<l>on the feet of him who put on [his] chest, garlanded with broad babul,</l>
<l>the girl, the woman Śrī from the ample lotus,</l>
<l>she yields, you with bright foreheads, my foolish offspring.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
